description:
Polimentor is a Google Partner Internet-marketing company, active on the market for more than 7 years. 
Our main services are: 
- Google Adwords (Search, Display network, Mobile campaign, Shopping campaign, Remarketing, Dynamic remarketing,Youtube advertising, Google Analytics) ;
- SEO (SEO audit, Top 10 Promotion,  Traffic promotion, Internal optimization);
- Social Media (Facebook/ Twitter/ Linkedin/ Instagram/Google+/Pinterest, Manage groups/pages, Advertising,  Forums posting, Crowd marketing);
- Content Writing;
- Email marketing;
- Web-analytics;
- Technical support;
- Landing page creation.
We have managed 3500+ successful advertising campaigns.
We work with a wide variety of businesses, including e-commerce, IT consulting, SEO firms, tourism, fitness and yoga centers and more, constantly expanding range of markets.
Polimentor is a result-oriented team of professionals, providing a full range of services in the sphere of internet marketing and e-commerce. Positive feedbacks from our partners only prove our commitment to the area we are working in.
